  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=626 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Hive</i> is a strategy game with RPG elements where you assume command as the insectoid hive mind. Set in a vast, ancient underworld filled with forgotten civilizations, colossal creatures, and untold mysteries, your journey is one of survival, evolution, and uncovering the secrets of a lost world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your colony grows, so does your understanding of the ruins scattered across New Eden, revealing a tragic history and a glimpse of what lies beyond. In this hostile yet beautiful landscape, danger and discovery go hand in hand, and every choice could shape the fate of your swarm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/8dcb800c59dacdd0a8bf5e04269b5dee.webp?t=1768824325\" width=640 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assume control as the insectoid hive mind and lead your swarm to survive and thrive in a vast, ruined underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/b63cc1684782b395f68b8c389f06b4b8.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and expand your underground nest to create a thriving colony and powerful forces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest DNA from defeated enemies to unlock new units, abilities, and strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip your creatures with powerful items scavenged from the remnants of lost civilizations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a850835446000fcbbc5d42fe7f1d8d7b.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle massive ancient creatures and adapt your strategy to overcome evolving challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience an epic story that spans the hostile, yet captivating, underworld of New Eden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/82d8da5ab479936d69574ddd60be00e2.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a beautiful yet dangerous world filled with ancient civilizations, mysterious ruins, and hostile creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover diverse biomes, from serene blooming springs to fiery volcanic regions, each filled with unique beauty and peril.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/895b6744dba6ab49bac55a2a7105e568.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.poster.avif?t=1768824325\" width=626 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.webm?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/a683cc3f34d26c8006451119c2a6c25f.mp4?t=1768824325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Hive</i> is a strategy game with RPG elements where you assume command as the insectoid hive mind. Set in a vast, ancient underworld filled with forgotten civilizations, colossal creatures, and untold mysteries, your journey is one of survival, evolution, and uncovering the secrets of a lost world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your colony grows, so does your understanding of the ruins scattered across New Eden, revealing a tragic history and a glimpse of what lies beyond. In this hostile yet beautiful landscape, danger and discovery go hand in hand, and every choice could shape the fate of your swarm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/325730/extras/8dcb800c59dacdd0a8bf5e04269b5dee.webp?t=1768824325\" width=640 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assume control as the insectoid hive mind and lead your swarm to survive and thrive in a vast, ruined underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store